{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The show was cancelled - but behind-the-scenes is a harrowing plot designed to destroy lives in the name of profit.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Spirits and other creatures\u00a0now lurk the abandoned set, leaving you unsure of who to trust.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Navigate the set, learn the truth behind the closure of the show,\u00a0and try to escape once and for all.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253140/extras/MH2Sawwy.gif?t=1734808723\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Desperate to escape the abandoned set, you strike a deal with a creepy android that is a replica of the star's show - Mint herself. You  agree to search the set for its lost power cores.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Armed with special ghost-hunting tools, you must navigate the haunted remnants of the set, discovering cryptic hints and recovering the android's missing pieces.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Can you collect all the hints and reactivate Android Mint before time runs out?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253140/extras/MH2GhostHunting.gif?t=1734808723\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Key Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">2 Hours of Playtime</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Ghost Hunting</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Obstacle Courses</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Cart Racing</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Lore &amp;\u00a0Story</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">VHS Cutscenes</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Voice Acting</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Made in Unreal Engine</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253140/extras/MH2VHS.gif?t=1734808723\" /></p>","background":"https://s